{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"toolu_vrtx_01WSTQdcdL7qVXs4qSNrR2Wk","content":"[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"JEM-94\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"New thread flow — start Amp session linked to an issue\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Wire `a` key in issue detail view to start a new Amp thread:\\\\n\\\\n1. Show workspace picker → user selects a directory\\\\n2. Snapshot thread IDs from `~/.local/share/amp/threads/`\\\\n3. Suspend ishi\\\\n4. Run `amp threads new` in the chosen directory\\\\n5. On resume, diff thread IDs to detect the newly created thread\\\\n6. If a new thread is found, save thread link (thread_id → issue_id + workspace) to state file\\\\n7. If no new thread detected (user exited without creating), do nothing gracefully\\\\n8. Restore TUI\\\\n\\\\nDepends on: workspace picker, suspend/resume, state file, amp thread reader.\\\",\\\"projectMilestone\\\":{\\\"id\\\":\\\"d2f17c9a-0039-4861-a5db-b44495d5ec6b\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Phase 5: Amp Integration\\\"},\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://linear.app/squareup/issue/JEM-94\\\",\\\"gitBranchName\\\":\\\"jmawson/jem-94-new-thread-flow-start-amp-session-linked-to-an-issue\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:28.424Z\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-03-18T04:51:44.781Z\\\",\\\"archivedAt\\\":null,\\\"completedAt\\\":null,\\\"dueDate\\\":null,\\\"slaStartedAt\\\":null,\\\"slaMediumRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaHighRiskAt\\\":null,\\\"slaBreachesAt\\\":null,\\\"slaType\\\":\\\"all\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"Backlog\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[],\\\"attachments\\\":[],\\\"documents\\\":[],\\\"createdBy\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"createdById\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"assignee\\\":\\\"Jeremy Mawson\\\",\\\"assigneeId\\\":\\\"f265a57f-26ba-4ba6-a014-a1414e9067c4\\\",\\\"project\\\":\\\"ishi\\\",\\\"projectId\\\":\\\"032af957-d258-43a4-9cac-246a45582daa\\\",\\\"team\\\":\\\"Jem\\\",\\\"teamId\\\":\\\"3dddde93-b00c-4573-a596-2475a0f69d3a\\\"}\"}]","is