{"type":"assistant","message":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done! よくできました (よくできました — well done)! Here's a summary:\n\n## Summary\n\nImplemented the new Amp thread flow (JEM-94) — pressing `a` in the issue detail view starts a new Amp session linked to that issue:\n\n**New components:**\n- **`WorkspacePicker`** (`app.rs`) — modal state with j/k navigation for selecting a workspace directory\n- **`snapshot_thread_ids`** (`amp/thread.rs`) — snapshots `*.json` filenames from the Amp threads directory as a `HashSet`\n- **`open_workspace_picker`** / **`start_new_thread`** (`main.rs`) — orchestration functions that load workspace history, suspend TUI to run `amp threads new`, diff thread IDs to detect the new thread, and save the link to state\n\n**Wiring:**\n- `a` key in both Body and Threads detail sections opens the workspace picker\n- Picker modal renders as a centered popup with `Clear` overlay\n- Enter confirms selection → snapshot → suspend → amp → diff → save state → reload threads\n- Esc cancels the picker\n- Status bar shows `a new thread` hint in both detail sections\n\n**Tests:** 11 new tests (100 total, all passing), covering `WorkspacePicker` navigation, `snapshot_thread_ids`, and `show/cancel_workspace_picker`."}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":661,"cache_read_input_tokens":108432,"output_tokens":321,"max_tokens":168000,"service_tier":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"T-019cff6b-1020-7104-aaed-de58f4c44518"}
